      <description>&lt;p&gt;Lab HW1, 2, and 3.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;h2 id=&#34;lab1-hw1-setup-blog&#34; class=&#34;heading-element&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;Lab1 HW1: Setup Blog&lt;/span&gt;&#xD;&#xA;  &lt;a href=&#34;#lab1-hw1-setup-blog&#34; class=&#34;heading-mark&#34;&gt;&#xD;&#xA;    &lt;svg class=&#34;octicon octicon-link&#34; viewBox=&#34;0 0 16 16&#34; version=&#34;1.1&#34; width=&#34;16&#34; height=&#34;16&#34; aria-hidden=&#34;true&#34;&gt;&lt;path d=&#34;m7.775 3.275 1.25-1.25a3.5 3.5 0 1 1 4.95 4.95l-2.5 2.5a3.5 3.5 0 0 1-4.95 0 .751.751 0 0 1 .018-1.042.751.751 0 0 1 1.042-.018 1.998 1.998 0 0 0 2.83 0l2.5-2.5a2.002 2.002 0 0 0-2.83-2.83l-1.25 1.25a.751.751 0 0 1-1.042-.018.751.751 0 0 1-.018-1.042Zm-4.69 9.64a1.998 1.998 0 0 0 2.83 0l1.25-1.25a.751.751 0 0 1 1.042.018.751.751 0 0 1 .018 1.042l-1.25 1.25a3.5 3.5 0 1 1-4.95-4.95l2.5-2.5a3.5 3.5 0 0 1 4.95 0 .751.751 0 0 1-.018 1.042.751.751 0 0 1-1.042.018 1.998 1.998 0 0 0-2.83 0l-2.5 2.5a1.998 1.998 0 0 0 0 2.83Z&#34;&gt;&lt;/path&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;&#xD;&#xA;  &lt;/a&gt;&#xD;&#xA;&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;p&gt;I utilize hugo to build the blog and Github Pages to host.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;I choose FixIt theme which is not bad. I am considering to switch to another theme to have preview photo in menu. Anyway, it doesn&amp;rsquo;t matter.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;h2 id=&#34;setup-hugo-and-theme&#34; class=&#34;heading-element&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;Setup hugo and theme&lt;/span&gt;&#xD;&#xA;  &lt;a href=&#34;#setup-hugo-and-theme&#34; class=&#34;heading-mark&#34;&gt;&#xD;&#xA;    &lt;svg class=&#34;octicon octicon-link&#34; viewBox=&#34;0 0 16 16&#34; version=&#34;1.1&#34; width=&#34;16&#34; height=&#34;16&#34; aria-hidden=&#34;true&#34;&gt;&lt;path d=&#34;m7.775 3.275 1.25-1.25a3.5 3.5 0 1 1 4.95 4.95l-2.5 2.5a3.5 3.5 0 0 1-4.95 0 .751.751 0 0 1 .018-1.042.751.751 0 0 1 1.042-.018 1.998 1.998 0 0 0 2.83 0l2.5-2.5a2.002 2.002 0 0 0-2.83-2.83l-1.25 1.25a.751.751 0 0 1-1.042-.018.751.751 0 0 1-.018-1.042Zm-4.69 9.64a1.998 1.998 0 0 0 2.83 0l1.25-1.25a.751.751 0 0 1 1.042.018.751.751 0 0 1 .018 1.042l-1.25 1.25a3.5 3.5 0 1 1-4.95-4.95l2.5-2.5a3.5 3.5 0 0 1 4.95 0 .751.751 0 0 1-.018 1.042.751.751 0 0 1-1.042.018 1.998 1.998 0 0 0-2.83 0l-2.5 2.5a1.998 1.998 0 0 0 0 2.83Z&#34;&gt;&lt;/path&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;&#xD;&#xA;  &lt;/a&gt;&#xD;&#xA;&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;ol&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;download &lt;a href=&#34;https://gohugo.io/&#34;target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;external nofollow noopener noreferrer&#34;&gt;hugo&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;create website:&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;/ol&gt;&#xA;&lt;div class=&#34;highlight&#34;&gt;&lt;div class=&#34;chroma&#34;&gt;&#xA;&lt;table class=&#34;lntable&#34;&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td class=&#34;lntd&#34;&gt;&#xA;&lt;pre tabindex=&#34;0&#34; class=&#34;chroma&#34;&gt;&lt;code&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;lnt&#34;&gt;1&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;lnt&#34;&gt;2&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;lnt&#34;&gt;3&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;lnt&#34;&gt;4&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;lnt&#34;&gt;5&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;lnt&#34;&gt;6&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&#xA;&lt;td class=&#34;lntd&#34;&gt;&#xA;&lt;pre tabindex=&#34;0&#34; class=&#34;chroma&#34;&gt;&lt;code class=&#34;language-bash&#34; data-lang=&#34;bash&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;cl&#34;&gt;hugo new site mr &lt;span class=&#34;c1&#34;&gt;# create frame in mr dir&lt;/span&gt;&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;cl&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;nb&#34;&gt;cd&lt;/span&gt; mr&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;cl&#34;&gt;get init&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;cl&#34;&gt;git submodule add https://github.com/hugo-fixit/FixIt.git themes/FixIt &lt;span class=&#34;c1&#34;&gt;# add theme&lt;/span&gt;&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;cl&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;nb&#34;&gt;echo&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;s2&#34;&gt;&amp;#34;theme = &amp;#39;FixIt&amp;#39;&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt; &amp;gt;&amp;gt; hugo.toml &lt;span class=&#34;c1&#34;&gt;# set the theme&lt;/span&gt;&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;cl&#34;&gt;hugo server &lt;span class=&#34;c1&#34;&gt;# view&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;/table&gt;&#xA;&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p&gt;I encountered a problem that some old theme is not compiled with the latest hugo. That&amp;rsquo;s one reason I choose FixIt.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;h2 id=&#34;publish-website&#34; class=&#34;heading-element&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;publish website&lt;/span&gt;&#xD;&#xA;  &lt;a href=&#34;#publish-website&#34; class=&#34;heading-mark&#34;&gt;&#xD;&#xA;    &lt;svg class=&#34;octicon octicon-link&#34; viewBox=&#34;0 0 16 16&#34; version=&#34;1.1&#34; width=&#34;16&#34; height=&#34;16&#34; aria-hidden=&#34;true&#34;&gt;&lt;path d=&#34;m7.775 3.275 1.25-1.25a3.5 3.5 0 1 1 4.95 4.95l-2.5 2.5a3.5 3.5 0 0 1-4.95 0 .751.751 0 0 1 .018-1.042.751.751 0 0 1 1.042-.018 1.998 1.998 0 0 0 2.83 0l2.5-2.5a2.002 2.002 0 0 0-2.83-2.83l-1.25 1.25a.751.751 0 0 1-1.042-.018.751.751 0 0 1-.018-1.042Zm-4.69 9.64a1.998 1.998 0 0 0 2.83 0l1.25-1.25a.751.751 0 0 1 1.042.018.751.751 0 0 1 .018 1.042l-1.25 1.25a3.5 3.5 0 1 1-4.95-4.95l2.5-2.5a3.5 3.5 0 0 1 4.95 0 .751.751 0 0 1-.018 1.042.751.751 0 0 1-1.042.018 1.998 1.998 0 0 0-2.83 0l-2.5 2.5a1.998 1.998 0 0 0 0 2.83Z&#34;&gt;&lt;/path&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;&#xD;&#xA;  &lt;/a&gt;&#xD;&#xA;&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;ol&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;create repo in github and name it username.github.io. Notice: keep it as a private repo. you can solve the authentication problem by at least three methods:&#xA;&lt;ol&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;repo-level token&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;user-level token&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;ssh authentication&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;/ol&gt;&#xA;&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;push the blog to the host&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;/ol&gt;&#xA;&lt;div class=&#34;highlight&#34;&gt;&lt;div class=&#34;chroma&#34;&gt;&#xA;&lt;table class=&#34;lntable&#34;&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td class=&#34;lntd&#34;&gt;&#xA;&lt;pre tabindex=&#34;0&#34; class=&#34;chroma&#34;&gt;&lt;code&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;lnt&#34;&gt;1&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;lnt&#34;&gt;2&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;lnt&#34;&gt;3&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;lnt&#34;&gt;4&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;lnt&#34;&gt;5&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;lnt&#34;&gt;6&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&#xA;&lt;td class=&#34;lntd&#34;&gt;&#xA;&lt;pre tabindex=&#34;0&#34; class=&#34;chroma&#34;&gt;&lt;code class=&#34;language-bash&#34; data-lang=&#34;bash&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;cl&#34;&gt;hugo &lt;span class=&#34;c1&#34;&gt;# build&lt;/span&gt;&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;cl&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;nb&#34;&gt;cd&lt;/span&gt; ./public &lt;span class=&#34;c1&#34;&gt;# the blog is built in ./public&lt;/span&gt;&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;cl&#34;&gt;git init&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;cl&#34;&gt;git add .&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;cl&#34;&gt;git commit -m init&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;cl&#34;&gt;git push -u origin main&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;/table&gt;&#xA;&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h2 id=&#34;lab1-hw2-and-3-unity-roll-a-ball&#34; class=&#34;heading-element&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;Lab1 HW2 and 3: Unity Roll-A-Ball&lt;/span&gt;&#xD;&#xA;  &lt;a href=&#34;#lab1-hw2-and-3-unity-roll-a-ball&#34; class=&#34;heading-mark&#34;&gt;&#xD;&#xA;    &lt;svg class=&#34;octicon octicon-link&#34; viewBox=&#34;0 0 16 16&#34; version=&#34;1.1&#34; width=&#34;16&#34; height=&#34;16&#34; aria-hidden=&#34;true&#34;&gt;&lt;path d=&#34;m7.775 3.275 1.25-1.25a3.5 3.5 0 1 1 4.95 4.95l-2.5 2.5a3.5 3.5 0 0 1-4.95 0 .751.751 0 0 1 .018-1.042.751.751 0 0 1 1.042-.018 1.998 1.998 0 0 0 2.83 0l2.5-2.5a2.002 2.002 0 0 0-2.83-2.83l-1.25 1.25a.751.751 0 0 1-1.042-.018.751.751 0 0 1-.018-1.042Zm-4.69 9.64a1.998 1.998 0 0 0 2.83 0l1.25-1.25a.751.751 0 0 1 1.042.018.751.751 0 0 1 .018 1.042l-1.25 1.25a3.5 3.5 0 1 1-4.95-4.95l2.5-2.5a3.5 3.5 0 0 1 4.95 0 .751.751 0 0 1-.018 1.042.751.751 0 0 1-1.042.018 1.998 1.998 0 0 0-2.83 0l-2.5 2.5a1.998 1.998 0 0 0 0 2.83Z&#34;&gt;&lt;/path&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;&#xD;&#xA;  &lt;/a&gt;&#xD;&#xA;&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;p&gt;It&amp;rsquo;s trivial to download unity and setup. But there is a small thing: the link provided in the HW instruction of the &lt;a href=&#34;https://learn.unity.com/tutorial/create-your-first-unity-project&#34;target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;external nofollow noopener noreferrer&#34;&gt;first-project&lt;/a&gt; is no longer available.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img loading=&#34;lazy&#34; src=&#34;https://zhe-xu-ipp.github.io/week2/week2tutorialnotavailable.png&#34; alt=&#34;/week2/week2tutorialnotavailable.png&#34; srcset=&#34;https://zhe-xu-ipp.github.io/week2/week2tutorialnotavailable.png?size=small, https://zhe-xu-ipp.github.io/week2/week2tutorialnotavailable.png?size=medium 1.5x, https://zhe-xu-ipp.github.io/week2/week2tutorialnotavailable.png?size=large 2x&#34; data-title=&#34;/week2/week2tutorialnotavailable.png&#34; style=&#34;background: url(/images/loading.min.svg) no-repeat center;&#34; onload=&#34;this.title=this.dataset.title;for(const i of [&#39;style&#39;, &#39;data-title&#39;,&#39;onerror&#39;,&#39;onload&#39;]){this.removeAttribute(i);}this.dataset.lazyloaded=&#39;&#39;;&#34; onerror=&#34;this.title=this.dataset.title;for(const i of [&#39;style&#39;, &#39;data-title&#39;,&#39;onerror&#39;,&#39;onload&#39;]){this.re